description:
Quizmine and RealSimpleEDU.com brings you "on-the-go" learning and reference for Computer Science 


App is continuously updated based on your feedback.


App offers 26 interactive tutorials and 8 quizzes with search.


Includes following tutorials:


Introduction,

Computer Fundamental,

Computer Hardware,

Computer Software,

Number System,

Introduction To Algorithms,

Searching Algorithms,

Introduction To Programming,

Introduction To Web Programming,

Object Oriented Programming,

Introduction To Java Programming,

Operating System,

Data Processing,

File Processing,

Data Structures,

Sorting And Sorting Algorithms I,

Sorting And Sorting Algorithms II,

Networking And Internet,

Databases I,

Databases II,

Software Engineering I,

Software Engineering II,

Data Communication,

Data Warehouse,

Memory Management,

Multimedia.


Our Vision: Provide on-the-go references that enable our customers to refer, learn and remember; easy to learn, more engaging and most complete.


Our Mission: A RealSimpleEDU app in every pocket.


Please write to us. We would love to improve this app.
